{"tid":1310564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一首歌印證香港呢廿年既倒退","createTime":"2019-07-12T17:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T17:41:59.000Z","uid":244845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0f3bc37dc4c17f8dffa1c65c9f3b3487a52390","tid":1310564,"uid":244845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://youtu.be/O82Y59EIFU8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO82Y59EIFU8&h=f45c2503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLMF 一首WTF<br />\n歌詞入邊既事理應講緊差唔多20年前既事<br />\n但歌詞都而家都岩用<br />\n社會應該越黎越進步<br />\n但香港呢廿年來不但冇進步過 仲每日退步<br />\n當時梁錦松偷步買車單野 用「一時大意」為由幫自己解釋<br />\n但最後自己辭職<br />\n到今日律政司大波驊知法犯法都可以冇事<br />\n真係wtf"},{"pid":"abed0a6d05ed4934da4e8e6da304f18c84389a63","tid":1310564,"uid":244845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:27:31.000Z","msg":"唔係佢地企得前<br />\n而係香港跟本不停咁退步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4189acc89036cbff8fd9cb39165da7786f6202f2","tid":1310564,"uid":244845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e3079cdb0abf0fef94667b89c67fa0fff2f0f6","tid":1310564,"uid":244845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a320f8edc680a9339af65ca81f141d4398ae7d8d","tid":1310564,"uid":244845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:37:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O82Y59EIFU8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO82Y59EIFU8&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80Bd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=00f7e6e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O82Y59EIFU8</a>"},{"pid":"ee3804d792aae1f0be37137d146f860e931a2325","tid":1310564,"uid":244845,"like":0,"disli